<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="79">On MEA at 25 °C colonies grow slowly, reaching 50 mm diameter within 50 d, at first pale yellow, gradually becoming dark brown with scanty aerial mycelium.</paragraph>
